# Block structure

```
blocks/<species>/<name>/
  contract.yaml
  core.ts
  layers/
    validation.ts
    security.ts
    observability.ts
  fixtures/
    test.yaml
```

- **species**: ingress, transform, validate, persist, emit, gate, query
- **Shared types** live in `shared/` — never import another block's core
- **Graph edges** live in `.blocks/graph.yaml` or `.blocks/graphs/<id>.yaml`
- **Full feature plan** — list all planned block ids in the graph YAML even before they are built; Studio and MCP read this file
- Block id must match path: `<species>.<name>`

When editing, load only the current block's contract and files.
